{"type": "article", "id": 12932, "title": "Motorola 蓝牙耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-03T07:40:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000218NzE7iyxnX5QSKBoJ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tMotorola 在刚刚过去的新品发布会上推出了两款新的蓝牙耳机，其中这款 “Moto Surround” 看上去颜值不错。这是款入耳式运动耳机，内置了一个可以续航12小时的电池，待机 30 天。采用防水防汗设计，可以支持通话和语音拨号，使用范围达到 46 米。同时，新耳机搭配了一个手机 App，可以自动确定耳机的位置，防止丢失。这款耳机售价 70 美元，这是<a href=\"https://www.motorola.com/us/accessories/music/wireless-headphones/moto-surround.html\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140621cbfgFiT2ePLX9VI3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140621x8vVgEdMepnwai5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140622Gc6nYNwMR2LosaIP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140622t4lmW6q1uj5VoE9F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140623ZbuWtV7m2HQjFSir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}